data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. This home has it all! Stunning dark hard surface floors beautifully contrast with the soothing neutral paint tones. The formal family and dining rooms provide the perfect backdrop for hosting memorable gatherings. The spacious living room is the heart of the home while the impressive kitchen boasts white cabinetry paired with granite countertops. The butler pantry and breakfast bar cater to all your culinary needs. Retreat to the primary suite with a cozy sitting area where you can savor your morning coffee. The ensuite bathroom is a spa-like escape, featuring separate vanities, a relaxing tub, and a separate shower. With a total of 6 spacious bedrooms, there's ample space to utilize each room to your liking. The upper loft and media room add versatility to the space, accommodating various lifestyles. Outside, the expansive patio offers abundant space for your outdoor furniture, perfect for al fresco dining and entertaining.
